 <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../831/29831.xml">
television</link> executive. He was born into a Jewish family in <village wordnetid="108672738" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../867/17867.xml">
London</link></village>
 of <country wordnetid="108544813" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
