i descent, and was educated at <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../647/2455647.xml">
The King's School, Ely</link>. After initially joining the <network wordnetid="108434259" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../654/19344654.xml">
