 and <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../388/8388.xml">
director</link> working on the high-profile <link>
documentary series</link>, <it><link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../593/3684593.xml">
Omnibus</link></it>, for which in 1975 he made a famous film called <it><product wordnetid="104007894" confidence="0.8">
<creation wordnetid="103129123" confidence="0.8">
<artifact wordnetid="100021939" confidence="0.8">
<event wordnetid="100029378" confidence="0.8">
